PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774966279
OL,3,CTributes to teenager killed in crash
OL,4,C"still helping others" as organ donor
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and attempting to
OL,9,Fpervert the course of justice.
OL,11,FA second man, aged 41, was also
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of perverting
OL,13,Fthe course of justice. Both men have
OL,14,Fbeen released under investigation.
OL,16,FPolice were called to the street in
OL,17,FGrimsby at around 6pm that evening
OL,18,Ffollowing reports of the collision,
OL,19,Fwith Lachlan taken to hospital to be
OL,20,Ftreated for life-threatening injuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
